Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.80,0:00:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.01,0:00:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.81,0:00:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.09,0:01:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.20,0:01:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不需的是要我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可以战斗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.34,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十七话\N[胜利和败北的轨迹]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，希洛仍然下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要笑，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N我现在也听到希洛的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，我相信他一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个山克王国出现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.77,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之后，过了多久呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从遇上他之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时，我和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.76,0:02:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起在前往地球的穿梭机里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我遇上包含了卫星\N的愿望的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切从这里开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动代号，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派给我的任务只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.37,0:04:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…\N我是莉莉娜‧德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之前的我只是一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没付出任何代价就享受幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知天高地厚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，遇上他后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.46,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的命运大大改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希洛‧唯，多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有错，是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要光临呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在流星作战里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只我一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重武装钢弹的驾驶者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠钢弹的驾驶者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔‧拿巴伯‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可以战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.62,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请别这样，因为是我先走出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停车!不停车我就攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩?少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这少年单人匹马攻击基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以很天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神龙钢弹的驾驶者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,张五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么光?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人!敌人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，死神钢弹的驾驶者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你在做什么?告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是鱼雷吧，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说话，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这情形怎样看\N你也比较像坏人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没受伤吧?小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别勉强啊，因为你是伤者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和这个人有何仇怨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，虽然好像有点内情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但立即离开这里比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是为了你的安全着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.90,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没当其他钢弹驾驶员是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，一开始我就没有同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个自称迪欧的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和莉莉娜一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是执行任务的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.85,0:09:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样，一切完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时，爸爸你强烈希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和卫星和平共存呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的报告我听过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望德利安外务次官你退席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经明言也无所谓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正危险的人是你们自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.36,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后\N爸爸带着我再次前往宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是爸爸你最后的关怀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了让我看美丽的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们想怎样处置我爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.62,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…不是…你真正的爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.86,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的真名是…\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是以前提倡和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特王族的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心OZ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.34,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…爸爸!你不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有关希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在圣米加勒学园的资料，取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转校手续，OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要去战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一个任务在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了你的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，比起我自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛是卫星派来的\N钢弹驾驶员一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许对于我的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.55,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有更大的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，我知道太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终要死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前不想一无所知就死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你战斗的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在也和希洛你在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个人应该死掉较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.35,0:13:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃避，我求你，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈统一联合最高司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔元帅\N希望和卫星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,计划想大幅裁军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，OZ的统帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以巧妙的情报手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令希洛他们齐集新爱德华基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后，借钢弹的手消灭联合军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别冲动啊，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二幕开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战名称[黎明行动]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场准备周详的政变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由布署在各地联合军基地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ士兵和SMS进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一日之内就令联合崩溃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.44,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就让你尝尝革命的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的时代已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要由我们OZ亲手创立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和新秩序一起建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着，OZ的上级特校蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提出了把宇宙用机动战士陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,运去西伯利亚基地的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那是一并歼灭钢弹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,声东击西战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他钢弹会来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我们应付不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，另外4个钢弹一定会来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相认定是最强敌人而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不接受这挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.92,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到有这么大威力的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络宇宙要塞巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各部钢弹的驾驶员听住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.63,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们准备好用飞弹\N攻击殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员现在马上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把钢弹交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星被瞄准了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我交出钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的要胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还能战斗吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不到你们是这么愚蠢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击卫星这等违反人道的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是不得已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里宣布投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但钢弹不能交出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，我投降\N但钢弹不能交出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务，明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也前往自己的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团想以名为支配的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,维持和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果继续战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那或许有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N在许多人牺牲后君临天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会容许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为山克王国的后裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星被当作挡箭牌就束手无策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，杰克斯修理好我的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.62,0:18:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望继续西伯利亚那场决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决斗的地点是南极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有接受杰克斯的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用特洛瓦的重武装钢弹决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.63,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这场决斗有何意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找寻要保护的东西的男人和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去保护办法的男人的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也会为过去\N所犯的错误而痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们还年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该想着创造未来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.67,0:19:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想结束这场无意义的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要那样才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在马上停止这场决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就用那双眼看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗有多污秽!有多卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是匹斯克拉福特的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没理由能做出那么卑鄙的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，诺茵特尉来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.76,0:20:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我误会了你是个更真诚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.97,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你鄙视也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.48,0:20:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会出言反对他想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!打倒杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.88,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么命运的安排也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望自己哥哥身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不经思考的想法，请你停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的王兄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次知道杰克斯是我王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多运输机从3时方向接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到吗?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.68,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是30部运输机\N包括艾亚利兹也只有100部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.28,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去引开他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光荣归于卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!后会有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后和我交手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杰克斯‧马吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁都好\N如果成为任务的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只好打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果始终是敌人，我就杀死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之后\N我就没见过哥哥和希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界踏上更混乱之途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，OZ一分为二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续着愚蠢的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了结束这场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定会在我的面前出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.32,0:22:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!快点回来我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.48,0:22:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.48,0:22:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.48,0:22:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.98,0:22:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.48,0:23:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.98,0:23:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.48,0:23:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.48,0:23:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要这个世上有人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.45,0:23:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗就绝对不会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.98,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而否定战斗不是和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.55,0:23:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达\N从历史的表面舞台消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.23,0:23:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯在不断交错的命运里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又即将显示新的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.53,0:23:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第二十八话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交错的命运

